them in the act.

00:16:06.210 --> 00:16:08.300
She burst through the
door with furious shouts

00:16:08.300 --> 00:16:12.290
for [inaudible] her barely
fair-haired, uncovered,

00:16:12.290 --> 00:16:15.980
