to N'angela must have been raised

00:16:23.860 --> 00:16:26.930
by a bitter woman who beat
him too hard and too often.

00:16:26.930 --> 00:16:29.730
His lackeys scurried
pitifully around him,

00:16:29.730 --> 00:16:34.620 position:56%
