up like a thread of smoke.

00:16:34.620 --> 00:16:38.040
His fist wrapped around a
stone Mama Lota had thrown.

00:16:38.040 --> 00:16:40.420
He spat and threw it back.

00:16:40.420 --> 00:16:44.290
