00:16:54.780 --> 00:16:57.580
Those thieving boys had broken
in through the one small window

00:16:57.580 --> 00:17:00.280
in the storehouse across
from the locked entrance.

00:17:00.280 --> 00:17:02.380
When Mama Lota toppled
across the threshold,

00:17:02.380 --> 00:17:04.780
