00:17:36.490 --> 00:17:39.250
Mama Lota liked to
remember him this way.

00:17:39.250 --> 00:17:42.390
Nearby, his mouth and
hands occupied.

00:17:42.390 --> 00:17:44.990
And now the glass and metal
thing that reminded her

00:17:44.990 --> 00:17:48.570
