00:18:45.140 --> 00:18:46.440
She stuck her teeth.

00:18:46.440 --> 00:18:48.440
"I don't know."

00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:49.790
N'angela shook her head.

00:18:49.790 --> 00:18:52.390
