knots where their tails had been.

00:19:24.620 --> 00:19:26.530
But they were not foolish.

00:19:26.530 --> 00:19:30.130
That was a sentimental view to
take about such vicious creatures.

00:19:30.130 --> 00:19:33.960
N'angela discovered how
vicious the very next morning.

