00:47:43.050 --> 00:47:44.440
It's okay."

00:47:44.440 --> 00:47:46.670
So that's happened a
couple of other times.

00:47:46.670 --> 00:47:48.110
"The Sack" as well.

00:47:48.110 --> 00:47:53.990
